  "text": "Multiple solutions were developed for the calculation of entropy of the data-row with finite length (like a representative sampling of physiological signals). These solutions are coherent with Shannon's entropy formulation. The Richman-Moorman entropy [CITATION_1] was applied to the analysis of multiscale entropy 1 , , , ,",
